    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ANIWARS is a strategic turn-based roguelike where you play as a faction Commander. Lead your squad, collect powerful items, conquer territory and face off against other powerful rival Commanders!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269540/extras/e1de1ff9946136cbff6652b75b483101.poster.avif?t=1765196652\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269540/extras/e1de1ff9946136cbff6652b75b483101.webm?t=1765196652\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269540/extras/e1de1ff9946136cbff6652b75b483101.mp4?t=1765196652\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >INNOVATIVE STRATEGIC COMBAT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle through difficult encounters where you must use everything at your disposal to prevail against the enemy, be it unique abilities, using the environment to your advantage, capturing objectives or finding the perfect use for the item you picked up earlier.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STORY &amp; FACTIONS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For over half a century, the world has been engulfed in an unending conflict. It all started after Void Day, a cataclysmic event where all of Vertex’s Dark Matter drives around the globe imploded creating Void Zones which swallowed cities and ripped apart continents. From the chaos three factions emerged: the Military, PUNKZ and Vertex. Each faction has its own style in both design and gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269540/extras/655b6e3129de8c958073dc1bb5884106.avif?t=1765196652\" width=1232 height=500 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE COMMANDERS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Commanders function both as playable characters and bosses! Each Commander has their own set of abilities and unique dialogue.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269540/extras/e1f4d030c3eeececf2b21c4ce2083dd5.avif?t=1765196652\" width=616 height=347 /></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CONQUER THE MAP</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Capture territory, gather resources and gain enough power to challenge the rival Commander at the end!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269540/extras/3b9b73a8322dc97df9e9a973ad4561d3.poster.avif?t=1765196652\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269540/extras/3b9b73a8322dc97df9e9a973ad4561d3.webm?t=1765196652\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269540/extras/3b9b73a8322dc97df9e9a973ad4561d3.mp4?t=1765196652\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >REPLAYABILITY!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lots of items and consumables with wild combos, events and dozens of battle maps make each run of ANIWARS a unique experience!  </p>",
